        \ | call SyntaxRange#Include('```c', '```', 'c', 'markdownCodeBlock')
        \ | call SyntaxRange#Include('```cpp', '```', 'cpp', 'markdownCodeBlock')
        \ | call SyntaxRange#Include('```lua', '```', 'lua', 'markdownCodeBlock')
